  "body": "Instead of \r\n```\r\nexample\r\n  .setValue(45)\r\n  .on('transactionHash', hash => {})\r\n  .on('receipt', receipt => {})\r\n  .on('error', error => {})\r\n  .on('confirmation', (num, receipt) => {})\r\n  .then(receipt => {});\r\n```\r\n\r\nWe can return an events object with all the promises as properties that can be awaited in line.\r\n```\r\nexample\r\n  .setValue(45)\r\n  .on('events\", events => {\r\n      const hash = await events.hash;\r\n      const receipt = await events.receipt;\r\n      etc...;\r\n   })\r\n```",
